// `emit_sections.vl` — the emitter's DRIVER and SECTION EMISSION: the
// `emitProgram` entry point with its ordered pass table, and the assembly of
// the final module bytes — header, type section (the one rec group), import/
// function/global/export/code sections, the shared runtime helper bodies
// (string hash/eq/concat, map probe/resize, mem-log), the start-function
// model for non-const globals, per-function code emission (`emitFuncCode`),
// and the opt-in name section. Sits ABOVE the lowering core (`wasmEmit.vl`),
// calling down into it for every statement/expression body. Carved out of
// `wasmEmit.vl` (review N18).

